lyrics:
(Verse 1) 
Empty rooms, echoing your name
A love unspoken, burning all the same
Haunted by memories, whispers in the air
Of promises unkept, a love I can't repair

(Chorus)
Lost in the darkness, searching for your light
A one-sided story, fading from sight
I build castles in the air, hoping you'll appear
But the only answer is the silence, loud and clear
style: Alternative rock, Alternative metal, Nu metal, Rap metal, Pop rock, Electronic rock, Rapcore,
